        <updateDate>2007-04-07T15:59:57Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Protecting Americans Fighting Terrorism Act of 2007 - Exempts individuals from civil liability for reporting suspicious behavior to federal, state, or local law enforcement agencies, if such reporting is made in good faith and with the reasonable belief that such behavior is suspicious.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
